{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Bonjour, also known as zero-configuration networking, enables automatic discovery of computers, devices, and services on IP networks. A wide range of Apple’s products-from iMacs and MacBooks to AirPort Base Stations and Time Capsules, Apple TVs to iPhones, iPod touches and iPads-use Bonjour for streamlined and reliable networking. Learn how to use Bonjour to make it easy for your applications to publish, discover, and resolve network services."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/211\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-211-bonjour-network-discovery-and-connectivity"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-211-Bonjour-Network-Discovery-and-Connectivity"},"metadata":{"title":"Bonjour Network Discovery and Connectivity","roleHeading":"WWDC11","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode"},"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC11":{"role":"collectionGroup","images":[{"type":"icon","iden